text: Manilkara pleeana, the zapote de costa, is a species of plant in the family Sapotaceae. It is endemic to Puerto Rico. ==References== pleeana Category:Plants described in 1891 Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Endemic flora of Puerto Rico Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by Jean Baptiste Louis Pierre Category:Taxa named by Henri Ernest Baillon Category:Taxa named by Arthur Cronquist
title: Manilkara pleeana
